{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"c04453f117bc52e8bc6152","title":"组二：时间戳 + 六种模式状态（本版全局参数）","desc":"","updated":1780371367065,"created":1780371330030,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.打印数据.02-本版-含模式状态","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"58623ede5983b7cd306383862c941193","links":[],"anchors":{"组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数":{"type":"header","text":"组二：时间戳 + 六种模式状态（本版全局参数）","value":"组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"纸上应出现的内容":{"type":"header","text":"纸上应出现的内容","value":"纸上应出现的内容","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"本版当前仓库speed5-全局参数纪要":{"type":"header","text":"本版（当前仓库）speed=5 全局参数纪要","value":"本版当前仓库speed5-全局参数纪要","line":30,"column":0,"depth":2},"与组一的差异便于分析":{"type":"header","text":"与组一的差异（便于分析）","value":"与组一的差异便于分析","line":46,"column":0,"depth":2},"归档建议":{"type":"header","text":"归档建议","value":"归档建议","line":51,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"b214abeb9f8f17aa994522","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数\">组二：时间戳 + 六种模式状态（本版全局参数）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数-1\">组二：时间戳 + 六种模式状态（本版全局参数）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#组二时间戳--六种模式状态本版全局参数-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"纸上应出现的内容\">纸上应出现的内容<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#纸上应出现的内容\"></a></h2>\n<p>在 <code>S</code> / <code>E</code> / <code>C</code> 下方追加模式块，例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">S:12345\nE:14123\nC:1778ms\nModes:\n* anime\n- cartoon\n- ink_wash\n- line_art\n- simple_drawing\n- sketch\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><code>* </code> 前缀：当前 UI 选中的模式  </li>\n<li><code>- </code> 前缀：其余五种模式（顺序与 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> 中 <code>s_mode_names[]</code> 一致）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"本版当前仓库speed5-全局参数纪要\">本版（当前仓库）speed=5 全局参数纪要<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#本版当前仓库speed5-全局参数纪要\"></a></h2>\n<p>对应 <code>applications/Printer/thermal_printer.c</code> 中 <code>apply_speed_profile()</code> 的 <code>default /* 5 fastest */</code> 分支及位图循环相关逻辑：</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>项</th><th>数值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>inter_group_us</code></td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td><code>line_cooling_us</code></td><td>10</td></tr><tr><td><code>heat_us_at_5c / 25c / 40c</code></td><td>1080 / 940 / 820</td></tr><tr><td><code>motor_step_us</code></td><td>650</td></tr><tr><td><code>status_check_period_lines</code></td><td>96</td></tr><tr><td>连续白行批量上限</td><td>96</td></tr><tr><td>周期性 <code>rt_thread_mdelay(1)</code></td><td>约每 256 行</td></tr><tr><td>位图结束后 <code>thermal_printer_feed</code></td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>高密度行额外加热（黑点档）</td><td>+135 / +90 / +55 / +28 / +10（分档）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"与组一的差异便于分析\">与组一的差异（便于分析）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#与组一的差异便于分析\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>纸上多出 <strong>Modes 文本块</strong>（由 <code>thermal_printer_print_text</code> → 内部再走位图，会略增加总时长与走纸，属正常现象）。  </li>\n<li>热参数与白行批量相对组一<strong>更激进</strong>，同图下 <code>C</code> 通常应 ≤ 组一；若画质下降，可对照两组样张与参数表回调。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"归档建议\">归档建议<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#归档建议\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>文件名建议：<code>YYYYMMDD_纸上Modes行首模式名_含Modes_备注.jpg</code>（与 <code>* </code> 行一致即可）。</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"个人开发笔记","desc":"个人开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e7a2abab31fd5da92a5ad2e013605349","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":41},"end":{"line":6,"column":9,"offset":47},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","i